Developers use images separately in development, but at debug/release phase, they often use packed texture. That means they need to change their code:

```
auto sprite = Sprite::create("image.png");
// to
auto sprite = Sprite::createWithSpriteFrameName("image.png");
```

It's better to let them keep the same code no matter they use packed texture or not.
